## GitHub Credentials

This project uses the same GitHub account as the parent `Noams_App` project.
The Personal Access Token (PAT) is stored in the parent repo's git config at:

```
c:\Users\razt\.cursor\projects\Noams_App\.git\config
```

The remote URL for this repo follows the same pattern:

```
https://<PAT>@github.com/RazTauber/Ninja_Timer.git
```

To extract the PAT from the parent, read the `[remote "origin"]` url from the parent's `.git/config` file.

## Git Setup (already done during initialization)

```bash
git init
git remote add origin https://<PAT>@github.com/RazTauber/Ninja_Timer.git
```

## Tech Stack

- Vanilla HTML + CSS + JavaScript
- Vite for dev server and bundling
- No framework -- intentionally simple
- CSV export via in-browser Blob/download
- localStorage for session persistence

## Important Notes

- When pushing or pulling, use the remote URL with the embedded PAT from the parent Noams_App repo.
- Never commit `.env` files or expose the PAT in committed files.
- The `.gitignore` is configured to exclude `node_modules/`, `dist/`, and `.env`.
